Rating: 2
Easy to make. Can go with the red peppers or just skip them, the marinate is what this recipe is all about. Marinate longer if able to and get your pan good and hot before you throw them on. Read recipe carefully because the vinegar is DIVIDED and this is not stated in the list of ingredients. Enjoy.

